set main (in stead of)

declare message "Use the modern single word `instead of` to indicate a replacement."
declare description "Corrects the archaic or mistaken separation `in stead of` to `instead of` in everyday usage."
declare kind "BoundaryError"
declare becomes "instead of"

test "He used water in stead of soda." "He used water instead of soda."
test "He used water instead of soda." "He used water instead of soda."
